<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Family Medication Management Invitation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            padding: 14px 28px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .features {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 12px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .app-links {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .app-links a {
            margin: 0 10px;
            color: #4CAF50;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Welcome to Family Medication Management</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
        
        <p>{{inviterName}} has invited you to join their family medication management group. This will help you stay connected and informed about your family's medication needs.</p>

        <div class="features">
            <h3>As a family member, you'll be able to:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>View shared medication schedules</li>
                <li>Receive important medication notifications</li>
                <li>Help manage medication inventory</li>
                <li>Stay updated on family medication needs</li>
                <li>Coordinate care with other family members</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <p style="text-align: center;">
            <a href="{{acceptUrl}}" class="button">Accept Invitation</a>
        </p>

        <div class="app-links">
            <p><strong>Get Started on Mobile:</strong></p>
            <a href="{{appStoreUrl}}">Download on iOS App Store</a> | 
            <a href="{{playStoreUrl}}">Get it on Google Play</a>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>This invitation will expire in 7 days.</p>
            <p>If you did not expect this invitation, please ignore this email.</p>
            <p>For support, contact us at {{supportEmail}}</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
